          "href": null,
          "name": "b2b6",
          "text": "Rancho Margot has begun construction of a village school that will host local children and also provide immersive learning experiences for adult practitioners. We will host our first workshop there in late January 2019 on the topic of “Managing Planetary Collapse” as part of the regenerative hub network.",
