        {
          "id": "b918f7ffd67_34",
          "href": null,
          "name": "7966",
          "text": "We are now taking steps to integrate the educational efforts of the many partners involved and weaving on-the-ground projects into frameworks of whole-system monitoring. Nothing less than the future of humanity is at stake and we take this call to action very seriously.",
          "metadata": null,
